text: Algert Gjonaj (born 18 October 1987) is an Albanian professional basketball player who plays for BC Vllaznia in the Albanian Basketball Superliga as well as the Albania national team.Përplasje në “Farie Hoti”, sulmohet Algert Gjonaj ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Albanian men's basketball players Category:Small forwards
title: Algert Gjonaj
